The '''Sarlacc Battalions''' were a formation within the [[41st Stormtrooper Legion|41st Elite Corps]] of the [[9th Assault Corps/Legends|9th Assault Corps]] in the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]].

In [[21 BBY/Legends|21 BBY]], [[Sarlacc Battalion A]] and [[Sarlacc Battalion B]] were deployed together as a [[Brigade/Legends|brigade]] on [[Dinlo]], led by [[Jedi General/Legends|Jedi General]] [[Vaas Ga]] and [[Clone Commander/Legends|Clone Commander]] [[Gree (clone trooper)/Legends|Gree]]. Encountering heavy [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droid]] opposition, they were [[Skirmish at Dinlo|extracted]] by the RAS ''[[Fearless]]''.

The overall fighting strength of the brigade consisted of 1152 men, i.e. the muster strength of two GAR battalions; of these ninety-four were killed on Dinlo, and 215 of the survivors were wounded.

